#: ../../F/feature-creature.rst:5
msgid "feature creature"
msgstr "feature creature"

#: ../../F/feature-creature.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../F/feature-creature.rst:9
msgid "[poss. fr. slang ‘creature feature’ for a horror movie]"
msgstr "[おそらくホラー映画を指すスラング‘creature feature’から]"

#: ../../F/feature-creature.rst:14
msgid ""
"One who loves to add features to designs or programs, perhaps at the expense"
" of coherence, concision, or :ref:`taste`\\."
msgstr "一貫性や簡潔さ、あるいは\\ :ref:`taste`\\ を犠牲にしてでも、設計やプログラムに機能を追加するのが大好きな人。"

#: ../../F/feature-creature.rst:17
msgid ""
"Alternately, a mythical being that induces otherwise rational programmers to"
" perpetrate such crocks. See also :ref:`feeping-creaturism`\\, "
":ref:`creeping-featurism`\\."
msgstr ""
"あるいは、ほかの点では理性的なプログラマーにそうした出来損ないを作らせてしまう、神話上の存在。\\ :ref:`feeping-"
"creaturism`\\ 、\\ :ref:`creeping-featurism`\\ も参照。"
